{"tid":2387723,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"忍屎大師 - 忍屎教學全攻略","createTime":"2021-01-30T14:07:46.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-31T02:41:42.000Z","uid":236080,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"5413d044f2247f01d6fd1cd9692a7fc7cea70872","tid":2387723,"uid":236080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T14:07:46.000Z","msg":"作者：忍屎大師<br />\n<br />\n多年北區翻港島長途車經驗，忍過火車地鐵巴士船。幾次差啲瀨，但最後都成功到自己心儀嘅廁所痾。作者我嘅腸胃好差，成日一上車冇耐就急屎，就算出門口之前痾一次先都冇用。<br />\n<br />\n忍屎最重要嘅只有2樣<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">心態</span></span></strong> <strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"blue\">毅力</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n失敗經驗：<br />\n<br />\n有幾次次忍唔住要落車去時代廣場痾屎，搞到遲到<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n急屎我會分三級：<br />\n<br />\n<ins>第一級 正常屎</ins><br />\n<br />\n正常屎意思係健康嘅屎，固體，水份唔多，所以亦係最易忍到嘅屎<br />\n<br />\n<ins>第二級 半爛屎</ins><br />\n<br />\n半爛屎意思係固體屎但係較碎，含水量比較多，一般而言只要有毅力都用適當方法，都可以忍到。<br />\n<br />\n<ins>第三級 爛屎</ins><br />\n<br />\n一般人稱之為「肚痾」，會糞便水狀，極臭，通常會想放屁個陣會feel到肛門口極之熾熱，非常非常難忍。<br />\n<br />\n忍屎方法：<br />\n<br />\n<ins>面對第一級</ins><br />\n<br />\n控制呼吸調節，通常痛個一下忍住過1-2分鐘就會放一下無聲臭屁，之後個肚會舒服30-45分鐘，一直循環。<br />\n<br />\n<ins>面對第二級 半爛屎</ins><br />\n<br />\n同樣要控制呼吸，但第一級嘅放屁方法可能會大大減低效力，因為今次含水量多啲啲，所以建議坐低，冷靜個人，用力緊握拳頭，但通常都會一直放屁跟住冇事咁循環。<br />\n<br />\n<ins>面對第三級 爛屎</ins><br />\n<br />\n呼吸一定要控制好，建議唔好玩電話，建議同人傾偈分散注意力。千祈唔好用放屁呢招，因為肛門口會熱到好似着火咁，啲屁都會臭到痴線，同埋有機會你放屁期間瀨少量屎。建議同樣手握拳頭，用指甲刮/插自己手掌/摵自己，令自己身體有其他痛楚，分散注意力。但建議要開始搵下附近邊到有廁所做最後準備，因為都凶多吉少。<br />\n<br />\n其實唔想肚痛，好簡單<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"gold\">上車 瞓覺</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n希望可以幫到大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d625bc5a70f20fa08d86e1ee8bc7aa0e065646eb","tid":2387723,"uid":236080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T14:08:55.000Z","msg":"咩為之忍屎失敗？<br />\n<br />\n就係瀨屎 / 忍唔住要落車痾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59b78d132420fe048f090054c884fe6208bff231","tid":2387723,"uid":236080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T14:14:41.000Z","msg":"冇人睇 唔通大家都唔洗忍屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10555b90ebc62f1e8407e5f6da4450f056080eac","tid":2387723,"uid":258921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T14:17:07.000Z","msg":"出街等車2,3級先驚<br />\n有車坐真係唔驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6390ef4fa7b7885a9f9cabd2d4914d07369f757f","tid":2387723,"uid":245711,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T14:17:45.000Z","msg":"個post好臭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9170a76a1c7b8ac63aaad44d5e9098b66587d38b","tid":2387723,"uid":44643,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T14:19:15.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">記得 記得<br />\n搭長途車<br />\n上車前<br />\n一定 一定<br />\n要睇地圖睇吓有冇塞先</span>"},{"pid":"da4e5958cac9279cbff76ec77f12c50d3e94407c","tid":2387723,"uid":236080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"10555b90ebc62f1e8407e5f6da4450f056080eac","tid":2387723,"uid":258921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T14:17:07.000Z","msg":"出街等車2,3級先驚<br />\n有車坐真係唔驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T14:20:46.000Z","msg":"等車仲有得救，上咗車亮大鑊<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2a09be7f9235ab4d50d443f93e32917f2224d2b","tid":2387723,"uid":236080,